thumb.title: 【Starry】Wake Up, Challenger!! [You Watanabe Solo Ver.]【踊ってみた】
thumb.description: Greetings, everyone! Today I have a cool song from Love Live Sunshine for you~This was a very special video that I filmed during one of my visits to the United States, my home country! I got to film this with help from a dear friend of mine on a beautiful spring day~It was warm in that leather jacket, but so worth it! Please enjoy it!I hope this video makes you smile, as much as it makes me smile when I think back on this amazing day.Together we can do anything!So let’s WAKE UP,MAKE UP for the whole world, CHALLENGERS!Sending you lots of love, until next time!Music and choreography by Aqours.Music reference for this version (You Watanabe solo): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GHWoo42sXFgMy choreo reference was this beautiful video! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zHi9YKjgRzkCamera by my good friend, Faith!★~Where to find me~★Twitter: https://twitter.com/starrylights13Instagram: @starrylights13 - https://www.instagram.com/starrylights13/?hl=enYouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/StarryLights13MyList: mylist/62719107
